<li id="cite_note-Vedomosti20101227-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Vedomosti20101227_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Vedomosti20101227_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Vedomosti20101227_6-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFПетрова2010" class="citation news cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source">Петрова, Светлана (Petrova, Svetlana) (27 December 2010). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20101229151158/https://www.vedomosti.ru/newspaper/article/252509/pensionnaya_shema">"Пенсионная схема: Можно ли использовать в своих интересах деньги пенсионеров так, чтобы Счетная палата не подкопалась? Способ есть"</a> &#91;Is it possible to use pensioners' money in their interests so that the Accounts Chamber does not undermine? There is a way&#93;. <i><a href="/wiki/Vedomosti" title="Vedomosti">«Ведомости»</a></i> (in Russian). Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.vedomosti.ru/newspaper/article/252509/pensionnaya_shema">the original</a> on 29 December 2010<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">21 October</span> 2021</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=%C2%AB%D0%92%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%C2%BB&amp;rft.atitle=%D0%9F%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F+%D1%81%D1%85%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B0%3A+%D0%9C%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%BD%D0%BE+%D0%BB%D0%B8+%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%82%D1%8C+%D0%B2+%D1%81%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B8%D1%85+%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%B0%D1%85+%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%8C%D0%B3%D0%B8+%D0%BF%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2+%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BA%2C+%D1%87%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8B+%D0%A1%D1%87%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F+%D0%BF%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B0+%